==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Rusine
<hw>Ru"sine</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[NL. <ets>rusa</ets>,
the name of the genus, Malay <ets>r⟦umac⟧sa</ets> deer.]</ety>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Of, like, or pertaining to, a deer of the genus
<gen>Rusa</gen>, which includes the sambur deer (<spn>Rusa
Aristotelis</spn>) of India.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Rusine antler</b></col> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>, <cd>an antler
with the brow tyne simple, and the beam forked at the tip.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Rusk</ent>⟦br⟧
